  "changelog": "2.4.0: aligned with the stable THSV StreamBridge 2.4.0 baseline, guided wizard UI, verified update metadata, and regenerated Streamer.bot imports. 1.0.0: initial cross-platform release with random, ID, search, count, viewer submission, moderator approval/rejection/edit, recoverable delete/restore, statistics, Twitch reply capture, exact ignores, bot/system/simulation/link gates, duplicate detection, cooldowns, bounded private storage, and optional creator controls.",
